    {
        "content": "<p>you can get injectivity from <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Data/Fintype/Card.html#Fintype.card_lt_of_surjective_not_injective\">Fintype.card_lt_of_surjective_not_injective</a>, by then i'm sure you can easily lift to equivalence...</p>",
